'desc': [u'

Locomotive Regular Fit Men's Jeans Price: Rs.650

Refresh your casual wardrobe by welcoming the Slim Fit Jeans from Locomotive designed for young men. The blue jeans is crafted from 100 per cent Cotton to provide you with ultimate comfort. This straight leg jeans is designed with a logo on the right pocket and an embroidery on the left pocket. The denim woven\xa0jeans features a coin pocket within right pocket and embroidered welt pockets at back. The low waist jeans is available in slim fit to give you a stylish and classy appearance.

Team this casual Locomotive Slim Fit Jeans with a Polo T-shirt and loafers when you head out for a party with your friends.\xa0Elevate the glam quotient of your wardrobe with denims from Locomotive that are a stylish coming together of the best fabric and sheer elegance. Go ahead
column13:
channel your inner fashionista.

Fabric Care

Treat this slim Fit Jeans with utmost care by washing it separately inside out. Do not dry clean or iron.

Locomotive Men's Striped Casual Shirt Price: Rs.520

Look classic and fashionable by wearing the Striped Youth Wear Shirt from Locomotive exquisitely designed for young men. Crafted from 100 per cent cotton
column13: this blue and red shirt with stripes is comfortable to wear. The Striped Shirt has embroidery on the left side of the chest and on the yoke. The logo on the pocket is added to make this shirt more stylish. The shirt also features foldable cuffs with contrast lining
column14:
a box pleat and curved hem with patch. This half-sleeved\xa0shirt comes with a slim fit that adds value to your personality.

You can style this casual Locomotive Striped Youth Wear Shirt with dark colored jeans and sneakers to look picture perfect.\xa0Contemporary tailoring and simplicity of design come together in Locomotive’s suave range of new-age casual shirts that cater to young men who are out to take the world by storm.

Fabric Care

Machine wash at 40 degree Celsius and tumble dry normal or line dry is preferred for a long life of the shirt. Do not bleach and wash dark colors separately.

\xa0

'desc': [u'

Locomotive Men's Striped Casual Shirt Price: Rs.727

Flaunt the fashionista in you by donning this striped and solid white shirt from the house of Locomotive. Crafted from 100 per cent cotton
column17: this casual shirt is tailored with an aim to keep comfort close to you the whole day. This half-sleeved shirt comes with an embroidery on the patch pocket and right sleeve
column18: a reverse stripe print in the front and epaulettes on the shoulder. Moreover
column19:
Locomotive has also fashioned this shirt with a curved hem and a hidden button placket.

Team this Locomotive Shirt with a pair of regular jeans and plimsolls. Carry a dapper look by carrying a sling bag along and wearing a smart watch. Channel your inner fashionista with casual shirts by Locomotive that embrace global style trends and put the spunk right back into your casual wardrobe.

Fabric Care

Machine wash this shirt with light colours. Tumble dry at normal temperature or line dry it. Use warm iron for a crisp look.
